            <title>[SOLR-4711] Fix Java 8 bugs in Solr Cloud tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4711</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some tests in Solr&apos;s cloud package always fail on Java 8. We should fix them before Java 8 comes out because its not a good idea to release a Solr distribution with a test that always fails.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
